name: Pearl - assemblage - 25/2013
description:
Porcelain dolls head, wood candlestick holder, vintage serviette ring, gold chain with filigree beads, chess piece, metal & plastic oddments, floral decoration, shells, resin starfish, plastic fish.  She has a tattoo across the right side of her head.

Pearl has sea green eyes and is seen walking along the beach each morning. Evidence of her accident has been tattooed giving her a unique look, a confidence in self. She epitomizes mending as a way of creating. 

17x5.5" (42x14cm) approximately
